title: Make this 3 Bed Apartment yours Cheaply
posting_body: ['Austin hotspots and Uptown energy infuse this apartment with an atmosphere that is ideal for adventure-seekers and young professionals alike.', 'Located in the North Austin area.', 'Enjoy amenities and perks like a fitness center with state-of-the-art equipment, a resident clubhouse with a business center, welcoming courtyards and more.', 'You’re sure to enjoy our two sparkling, resort-style pools, which are accompanied by gorgeous landscaping and plenty of comfortable seating, as well as community gas grill areas perfect for barbecues and get-togethers.', 'Our friendly staff and maintenance teams are always ready to assist with resident needs, which is an amenity in itself.', 'Pet friendly as well, with two dog parks, green spaces, area parks and walking trails.', 'We welcome a variety of breeds and allow up to two pets per apartment home.', 'Choosing your home is important.', 'With finishes and wide-open spaces, this apartment brings you style without sacrificing on comfort.', 'Features and amenities include wood-style flooring, updated fixtures, sleek countertops, new appliances, modern palettes, oversized sinks and counter areas, roomy closets and so much more.', 'Don’t settle for less when it comes to apartment living.', 'Treat yourself right.', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'ID:  132', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', 'Touring recommended, after consult with above agent.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
